      {
        "description": "The Dragino LT22222-L is a LoRaWAN® I/O module that contains different I/O Interfaces such as analog current input, analog voltage input, relay output, digital input, and digital output. The LT series I/O modules are designed to simplify the installation ",
        "enabled": true,
